column1: #Unit Name - Identifying unique name for the unit. Mandatory.
#Dpsk Secret - Dpsk passphrase for unit users. Optional
#Unit Vlan - Vlan for unit users.This must be a number in range 0-4096. Optional
#Guest Dpsk Secret- Dpsk passphrase for guest users. Optional
#Guest Vlan - Vlan for guest users. This must be a number in range 0-4096. Optional
#Email - Email address of the resident. Optional
#Phone Number - Phone number of the resident. Format +<country code><phone number>. Optional
